{"tid":272443,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁小氣？】比基諷刺皇馬：我們出局都有掌聲","createTime":"2017-06-05T23:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T23:29:33.000Z","uid":47303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a630050eb9d8f129015f6c529eca9f7543c0be1e","tid":272443,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:05:30.000Z","msg":"在首回合0-3輸波的情況下，巴塞次回合拚盡全力，依然無力回天。雖然球隊被淘汰出歐冠盃，但魯營現場的球迷還是為巴塞球員送上了掌聲。 <br />\n<br />\n　　《馬卡報》賽後組織了一次討論：在球隊出局的情況下，依然為球隊鼓掌，魯營球迷的行為是正確的嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n　　比基在Twitter上加入了討論，這一次他依然沒忘記嘲諷一下死敵皇馬：「對有些人來說，看到魯營球迷在球隊出局時依然送上掌聲，是一件很難受的事情。（在班拿貝）他們已經習慣了聽到球迷的噓聲，即使球隊晉級。」"},{"pid":"7f7dad28dc779ba755698c6640fe8b85ee1723b8","tid":272443,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"鳩白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩呢排貢猛既"},{"pid":"2f992d3303bf12a4359586d7484c8df24f748744","tid":272443,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:35:18.000Z","msg":"比d掌腥自己!"},{"pid":"64fca6eb4e0a7cdeb374ea7b9ad8d2e7ef626651","tid":272443,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:40:51.000Z","msg":"c朗諷刺碧基：我續約都有掌聲"},{"pid":"75fee13884904b47b078a6c83881c8d265a28f99","tid":272443,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩呢排貢猛既</blockquote><br />\n佢忍左成季<br />\n宜家完左季終於可以衝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56594fc140b7a75caf99b6c85fedbaa44327461","tid":272443,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23: